      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Presenting a true collector-grade example that defies its age. This vehicle has been meticulously preserved in a climate-controlled garage and shows like it just rolled off the showroom floor. The exterior features original, deep-gloss paint with zero swirl marks, protected by a professional-grade ceramic coating. Every body panel is laser-straight with perfect factory gaps. Inside, the cabin remains pristine; the premium leather seats show no bolster wear, and the dashboard is free of any UV damage or fading. Mechanically, it is flawless. It comes with a complete, documented service history from day one, with all preventative maintenance performed ahead of schedule. There are no leaks, no squeaks, and the engine pulls with the same smoothness it had when new. This is a turn-key investment for a discerning buyer who demands perfection and wants a vehicle that needs absolutely nothing.",
